Step 1: Start
Step 2: Move Input Address to DPTR
Step 3: Move Value of DPTR to Accumulator
Step 4: Move Accumulator Value to R0
Step 5: Increment DPTR
Step 6: Move Value of DPTR to Accumulator
Step 7: Move Accumulator Value to R1
Step 8: Increment DPTR
Step 9: Move Value of DPTR to Accumulator
Step 10: Move Accumulator Value to R2
Step 11: Increment DPTR
Step 12: Move Value of DPTR to Accumulator
Step 14: Move Accumulator Value to R3
Step 14: Increment DPTR
Step 15: Clear Carry
Step 16: Move R0 to Accumulator
Step 17: Add R2 and Accumulator
Step 18: Store Accumulator Value in DPTR
Step 19: Increment DPTR
Step 20: Move R1 to Accumulator
Step 21: Add Accumulator and R3
Step 22: Store Accumulator Value in DPTR
Step 23: Increment DPTR
Step 24: If No Carry Go to Step 27
Step 25: Store 01 in Accumulator
Step 26: Move Accumulator Value to DPTR
Step 27: Stop